Hi, 

I am considering dropping a CS class in the summer after the refund deadline. But it seems that I was not allowed to on CalCentral. I have already submitted the LS late drop form. Is there any other thing I need to do? 

For financial aid, I need to maintain at least 6 units to be considered. Can I ask another class for Tuition Credit to get a minimum of 6 units? Is there anything I need to be cautious when doing this? Thanks.
